 complement conventional INS\nmeasurements of the dispersion at constant field and holds great promise for\nidentifying the symmetry of multipolar order parameters and the details of\ninter-multipolar interactions that stabilize hidden-order phases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jan 2020 17:18:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-15"}
